                     >June 13, 1735</date>, in <placeName>Miserton, Nottinghamshire</placeName>.
                  Harper proved inept at holding a job, and mainly interested in <persName><ref
                        target="/persons/pers2179.xml"/>Emilia</persName>&apos;s financial
                  resources. Within a few years they were separated and <persName><ref
                        target="/persons/pers2179.xml"/>Emilia</persName> living in
                     <placeName>London</placeName>. See Maser, <hi rend="italic">Sisters</hi>,
